Time Complexity
push() → O(n) (queue rotate karna padta hai)
pop() → O(1)
top() → O(1)
empty() → O(1)

Space Complexity
O(n) (queue me n elements store hote hain)

Approach: Queue me element insert karke queue ko rotate kar dete hain taaki latest element front par aa jaye aur stack ka LIFO behavior achieve ho